modName: Armor of Talos and Cake Knife
summary: Adds a banded iron armor set call "Armor of Talos" and a new ebony sword called "Cake Knife".
descriptionHtml:
Armor of Talos is made at a forge under Iron Smithing. The Cake Knife is made under Ebony Smithing. Have fun winning your battles! My first mod and more soon to come!
Youtube channel: that3picgam3r

Have any Questions? leave in comments ill try my best to [url=#]answer[img]http://cdncache-a.akamaihd.net/items/it/img/arrow-10x10.png[/img][/url] them.
